<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Te digo tó y no te digo ná: Termodinámica + Teoría de la Información | CORTEX Persist</title>
    <meta name="description" content="El 0.002% de la población mundial posee una comprensión operativa profunda de la termodinámica estadística y la teoría de la información de Shannon-Jaynes. Una estimación Fermi y criterio técnico.">

    <!-- Google Fonts: Outfit & JetBrains Mono -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            /* Industrial Noir 2026 Color Palette */
            --ember-void: #0A0A0A;
            --yinmn-blue: #2B3BE5;
            --sovereign-amber: #FF9F1C;
            --oxide-gold: #FFD700;
            --parchment-white: #F3F4F6;
            --crimson-accent: #FF0055;
            --neon-cyan: #00E5FF;
            --glass-bg: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.75);
            --mica-dust: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.05);
            --mica-border: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.15);
            --crimson-border: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.15);
            --amber-border: rgba(255, 159, 28, 0.15);

            /* Typography */
            --font-primary: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;

            /* Transitions */
            --transition-smooth: all 400ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            --radius-soft: 12px;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--ember-void);
            color: var(--parchment-white);
            font-family: var(--font-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Analog Grain Overlay */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noiseFilter'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noiseFilter)' opacity='0.045'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
            opacity: 0.75;
        }

        /* Ambient Glow Shadows */
        .ambient-glow {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 1000px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.12) 0%, transparent 65%),
                        radial-gradient(ellipse at center 20%, rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 120px 24px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .back-nav {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .back-nav a {
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .back-nav a:hover {
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            margin-top: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #B5B5B5 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.6);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .meta {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .meta-tag {
            background: var(--mica-dust);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .meta-tag--crimson {
            border-color: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.4);
            color: var(--crimson-accent);
            background: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.06);
        }

        /* Section Headings */
        h2 {
            font-size: 2.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 60px 0 24px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        h2::before {
            content: "◈";
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--parchment-white);
            margin: 36px 0 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.85);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        strong {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        code {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            background: var(--mica-dust);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        /* Blockquotes */
        .quote-block {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.45;
            color: var(--parchment-white);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--yinmn-blue);
            padding: 24px 32px;
            margin: 48px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--mica-dust) 0%, transparent 100%);
            border-radius: 0 var(--radius-soft) var(--radius-soft) 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .quote-block--crimson {
            border-left-color: var(--crimson-accent);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.04) 0%, transparent 100%);
        }

        /* Glassmorphic Tables */
        .table-container {
            width: 100%;
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 32px 0;
            border-radius: var(--radius-soft);
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.08);
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
        }

        td {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.8);
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        tr {
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        tr:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
        }

        /* Divider */
        .section-divider {
            width: 60px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--yinmn-blue), transparent);
            margin: 60px 0;
        }

        /* Lists */
        ul, ol {
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        li {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.85);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 28px;
            position: relative;
            list-style: none;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        ul li::before {
            content: "→";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
        }

        ol {
            counter-reset: custom-counter;
        }

        ol li {
            counter-increment: custom-counter;
        }

        ol li::before {
            content: "0" counter(custom-counter) ".";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.3);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #5C6BF0;
            border-bottom-color: #5C6BF0;
        }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------
           INTERACTIVE COMPONENT: FERMI FUNNEL
           ------------------------------------------------------------- */
        .funnel-widget {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-soft);
            padding: 28px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .funnel-widget {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .funnel-visuals {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .funnel-stage {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .funnel-stage::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--yinmn-blue);
            opacity: 0.05;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .funnel-stage[data-width="1.0"]::after { width: 100%; }
        .funnel-stage[data-width="0.1"]::after { width: 10%; }
        .funnel-stage[data-width="0.02"]::after { width: 2%; }
        .funnel-stage[data-width="0.0004"]::after { width: 0.4%; }
        .funnel-stage[data-width="0.00002"]::after { width: 0.002%; }

        .funnel-stage:hover, .funnel-stage.active {
            border-color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            background: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.08);
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .funnel-stage:hover::after, .funnel-stage.active::after {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }

        .funnel-stage.active-crimson {
            border-color: var(--crimson-accent);
            background: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.08);
        }

        .funnel-stage.active-crimson::after {
            background: var(--crimson-accent);
            opacity: 0.2;
        }

        .funnel-dashboard {
            border-left: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding-left: 24px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .funnel-dashboard {
                border-left: none;
                border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
                padding-left: 0;
                padding-top: 20px;
            }
        }

        .dash-title {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .dash-number {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.3);
        }

        .dash-number.crimson-text {
            color: var(--crimson-accent);
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.3);
        }

        .dash-details {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.6);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .dash-math {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--sovereign-amber);
            background: rgba(255, 159, 28, 0.05);
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
        }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------
           INTERACTIVE COMPONENT: ENTROPY SANDBOX
           ------------------------------------------------------------- */
        .sandbox-widget {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-soft);
            padding: 28px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .sandbox-controls {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .sandbox-slider-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .sandbox-slider-container label {
            width: 140px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.7);
        }

        .sandbox-slider {
            flex-grow: 1;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            outline: none;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 2px;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .sandbox-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--yinmn-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.5);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .sandbox-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover {
            transform: scale(1.25);
        }

        .sandbox-val {
            width: 60px;
            text-align: right;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .sandbox-displays {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .sandbox-displays {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .sandbox-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sandbox-card h4 {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .sandbox-card-num {
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sandbox-card-num--cyan {
            color: var(--neon-cyan);
        }

        .sandbox-card-formula {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.5);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
        }

        /* Microstate Particle Canvas Representation */
        .sandbox-canvas-container {
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            height: 120px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .sandbox-particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--yinmn-blue);
            opacity: 0.4;
            transition: transform 5s ease-in-out, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sandbox-particle.state-1 {
            background: var(--neon-cyan);
        }

        .sandbox-canvas-label {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 12px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.3);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------
           INTERACTIVE COMPONENT: LANDAUER CHAMBER
           ------------------------------------------------------------- */
        .chamber-widget {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-soft);
            padding: 28px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .chamber-widget {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .chamber-column-left {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .chamber-slider-box {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .chamber-slider-box label {
            display: block;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.6);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .chamber-btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--crimson-accent);
            color: var(--crimson-accent);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .chamber-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.25);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .chamber-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }

        .chamber-column-right {
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #000;
            height: 220px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .chamber-partition {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            width: 2px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            z-index: 2;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .chamber-partition.closed {
            background: var(--crimson-accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.6);
        }

        .chamber-demon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: calc(50% - 15px);
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.4);
            z-index: 3;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
        }

        .chamber-demon.glow-crimson {
            background: rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.2);
            border-color: var(--crimson-accent);
            color: var(--crimson-accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--crimson-accent);
        }

        .chamber-heat-flash {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: var(--crimson-accent);
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.1s ease;
        }

        .chamber-particle-c {
            position: absolute;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--yinmn-blue);
            transition: left 0.5s ease-in-out, top 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .chamber-info-pane {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 12px;
            left: 12px;
            right: 12px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            z-index: 4;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.8);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        /* -------------------------------------------------------------
           FOOTER TERMINAL
           ------------------------------------------------------------- */
        .footer-terminal {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 24px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid var(--mica-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-soft);
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(243, 244, 246, 0.6);
        }

        .terminal-line {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .terminal-prompt {
            color: var(--yinmn-blue);
        }

        .terminal-success {
            color: #10B981;
        }

        /* Selection */
        ::selection {
            background: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.3);
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="ambient-glow"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="back-nav">
            <a href="/blog">← Intelligence Log</a>
        </div>

        <header>
            <div class="meta">
                <span class="meta-tag">#C5-REAL</span>
                <span class="meta-tag meta-tag--crimson">ensayo</span>
                <span>Telmo Dinámico de Moskv</span>
                <span>Junio 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h1>Te digo tó y no te digo ná</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Termodinámica + Teoría de la Información</p>
        </header>

        <div class="quote-block quote-block--crimson">
            "Todo bit de información posee un coste físico equivalente en entropía. La computación pura no existe al margen de la física de partículas: borrar es disipar."
        </div>

        <!-- Section 1: Intro / claim -->
        <p>En el panorama de la informática agéntica moderna, la tendencia natural es abstraer la infraestructura de silicio y tratar el procesamiento de datos como un reino etéreo de lógica abstracta. Sin embargo, toda computación ocurre en el mundo físico y está ligada a leyes inviolables.</p>
        
